name: Harvest MicroStrategy High Income Shares ETF
longDescription: In order to achieve its investment objectives, Harvest MicroStrategy High Income Shares ETF will invest up to 100% of its total assets in the common stock class A of MicroStrategy and will write covered call options on shares of MicroStrategy. The proportion of covered call options written will vary depending on market conditions and will be based on the Harvest ETFs distribution policy, subject to a maximum 50% write level. The Harvest ETFs covered call strategy will be reviewed monthly to ensure cash flow sustainability according to the Harvest ETFs distribution policy.
